    <section class="section-padding article white-section">
        <div class="wrapper">
    
            <h2 class="section-heading">Travel Insurance – Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    
            <div class="faq">
    
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        Do I need travel insurance?
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Travel insurance is strongly recommended for all trips, as it helps protect against unexpected
                            events such
                            as medical emergencies, trip cancellations, lost baggage, and travel delays both in the UK and
                            abroad.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        What does travel insurance usually cover?
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Travel insurance typically includes cover for emergency medical treatment, trip cancellation or
                            curtailment,
                            lost or stolen baggage, personal liability, and 24/7 emergency assistance. Cover varies
                            depending on the
                            policy and insurer.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        Is travel insurance mandatory?
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Travel insurance is not legally required; however, it is highly recommended, particularly when
                            travelling
                            abroad, due to the high cost of medical treatment and potential travel disruption.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        Can I get cover for business travel?
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Business travel insurance is available and can include cover for work-related travel, such as
                            medical
                            emergencies, delays, and business equipment, depending on the policy terms.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
            </div>
    
